{"tid":657765,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"IT科技人才入境計劃 => 政府APII AP是垃圾","createTime":"2018-05-08T11:18:14.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-17T05:40:06.000Z","uid":64694,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"2eea8d9fcca7f108455d6f322a2c72ed4f3e702b","tid":657765,"uid":64694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T11:18:14.000Z","msg":"如果政府班APII AP係科技人才，咁點解重要引入科技人才嚟香港呢？用返佢哋咪得囉，所以呢樣嘢似乎講唔通喎<br />\n<br />\n由此推斷，政府班APII AP根本係垃圾嚟，而家唔係我話你哋，而家係政府根本唔放你哋在眼內，直接用「科技人才入境計劃」形容你哋唔係科技人才，大陸班人都勁過你哋，點解你哋重要留喺一個睇唔起你哋嘅政府做嘢？重留係入面工作咪即係你哋都承認自己係垃圾？<br />\n<br />\nBTW，第時政府請APII可能剩係會請大陸班所謂「科技人才」<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc9fe7c6fdfb07da29a2b92ef0da4bc5ae606d10","tid":657765,"uid":64694,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T11:24:40.000Z","msg":"莫乃光指科技人才計劃可能引入經驗淺人才<br />\n<br />\n政府推出「科技人才入境計劃」，為輸入海外和內地科研人才，實施快速處理安排，立法會資訊科技界議員莫乃光，對於申請者的經驗要求有保留，認為應該提高標準。<br />\n<br />\n他認為，引入的可能是經驗淺的人才，但香港公司缺乏的是有五至七年工作經驗的人士，這些輸入的人士不能做到「師傅帶徒弟」的作用，亦會對本地畢業生構成競爭。他認為，政府在推行計劃的同時，應協助本地人才升級轉型，令他們能在行業繼續健康發展。<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n按政府的計劃，來港人士須持有具特別認受性的大學所頒授的科學、科技、工程或數學（STEM）學科學位，持有碩士或博士學位者毋須工作經驗，持有學士學位者則須具備最少一年在相關科技範疇的工作經驗。 </span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1395280-20180508.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1395280-20180508.htm&d=kITmQhX2jxy5zroRDY4WqBxMMk18geApnjdPrdglKpk%3D&h=ebcfcb09\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1395280-20180508.htm&h=edccd744\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1395280-20180508.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">咁叫人才喎，嚟爭飯食就差唔多，同香港嘅CS畢業生根本無分別</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9019bae5afcbfafb39e335d87f2674d3caeedce","tid":657765,"uid":64694,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T11:49:02.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=305071\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D305071&d=kITmQhX2jxy5zroRDY4WqBxMMk18geApnjdPrdglKpk%3D&h=3d732627\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D305071&h=a325c299\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=305071</a>"},{"pid":"02d1338a3aa1fd7bae0b96d873051e8026a1ece6","tid":657765,"uid":57705,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T11:54:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f140082b86186319963f5a713ab62d8b5d57e50a","tid":657765,"uid":64694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T15:30:32.000Z","msg":"好話唔好聽如果嗰1000個人喺香港搵唔到工，政府可能要硬食請返嗰堆人做APII，到時香港班人想入去做APII都難，人哋拎住「科技人才」個term去申請，可能面試筆試都唔使就直入（入咗你都唔知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，內部已經搞掂），好似班新移民嚟到香港即刻有新公屋咁，香港嗰班重要死磨爛磨個筆試同面試都未必有機<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33c3061fdb5c94215664e828ca667a20684ae5f7","tid":657765,"uid":13592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T15:45:32.000Z","msg":"老老柒柒 未work過掂嘅蝗"},{"pid":"c689f9f34217c111d7326741a6c976c13ae13915","tid":657765,"uid":132965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T08:49:42.000Z","msg":"要唔要考CRE?"},{"pid":"9a4cf2925f8ca5c1dada0f1a3d94768668eea536","tid":657765,"uid":64874,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"c689f9f34217c111d7326741a6c976c13ae13915","tid":657765,"uid":132965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"reply